commitResults.messageBody:
1) Delete DukeOperator, abstract individual commands to classes AddCommand, DeleteCommand, ExitCommand, ListCommand, DoneCommand.
2) Add enum AddCommandType to support AddCommand for different Task types.
3) Delete enum Operation.
4) Rename DukeInputProcessor to Parser. Parser now outputs a Command instead of an enum Operation.
5) Abstract Storage (loading and saving from savefile) from DukeOperator.
6) Rename TaskStorage to TaskList. TaskList operations do not return a confirmation string anymore.
